metadata.name: ZATHENIAN STAFF LION #01
metadata.description: The OFFICIAL Staff Collection for Zathena Ventures, LLC and it's respective projects such as the Lions of Zathena. These pieces are custom Lions that represent a dedication to the team and onboarding into the tight-nit family that makes the pride keep moving forward! Team members may come and go, but this NFT shows that they put in their time and worked to make Zathena a better jungle for all Lions!
